        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for <hi rend="italic">Megarrhiza</hi> seeds and information. Has been greatly interested by <hi rend="italic">Megarrhiza</hi> germination.</p>  
<p>Samuel Butler has attacked CD over <hi rend="italic">Erasmus Darwin</hi>.</p> 
